@page "/first-page/{abc:int?}"
<h1 style="color: red;">This is the first Razor Page</h1>
<p>Learn ASP.NET Core <strong>(@System.DateTime.Now)</strong></p>

@{
  int a = 4;
  int b = 5;
  <p>Square root of @a is @Math.Sqrt(a)</p>
}

<p>Sum of @a and @b is @(a + b)</p>

<ol>
  @for (int i = 0; i <= b; i++)
  {
    <li>Number: @i</li>
  }
</ol>

@{
  var abcString = this.Request.RouteValues["abc"]??"0";
  int abc = Int32.Parse(abcString.ToString());
  <p>The value of abc: @abc</p>
}